Only 2 Steps to Start Angular2. Follow these Steps.
1)npm install
2)npm start

Reference:
https://angular.io/docs/ts/latest/quickstart.html

Copy Paste the Angular2 folder to your local.
Go to the Angular2 dir in command prompt 

1) D:\angular2>npm install

Check the folder Structure 
angular2
	node_modules ...
	typings ...
	package.json
	systemjs.config.js
	tsconfig.json
	typings.json
	
  If the typings folder doesn't show up after running npm install, you'll need to install it manually with the command:
  1.2) D:\angular2>npm run typings install

2) D:\angular2>npm start


The final project folder structure looks like this:
angular2
	app
		app.component.ts
		app.module.ts
		main.ts
	node_modules ...
	typings ...
	index.html
	package.json
	styles.css
	systemjs.config.js
	tsconfig.json
	typings.json
